        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[v0.30.0]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[## ⚠️ Notice * The Tabby Docker image now requires an NVIDIA GPU. For CPU-only environments, use the Linux binary. ## 🚀 Features * Support indexing GitLab Merge Request as Context. #4227 ## 🧰 Fixed and Improvements * Use CUDA 12 image as base image by default. #4235 * Leverage the Answer Engine logic to enrich the context when generating new pages, improving page quality. #4237 * Improve the model configuration details on the System page. #4236 * Resolve the flickering of buttons within code snippets in a chat response during answer generation. #4233 * Set the member filter bar always fixed at the top of the Reports page.#4232 * Resolve the issue when loading a multi-part model from local.#4302 ## 💫 New Contributors * @petarjuki7 made their first contribution in #4265 **Full Changelog**: https://github.com/TabbyML/tabby/compare/v0.29.0...v0.30.0]]></description>
            <link>https://github.com/TabbyML/tabby/releases/tag/v0.30.0</link>
